description: Inferno subs is getting thousands of Wisconsin foodies all fired up about their most delightful toasted gourmet sandwiches. This truck offers a magnificent menu that features a searing selection of sandwiches, including BBQ Chicken, Spicy Italian Club, and Southwest Chicken with Bacon - and it must be mentioned that their best selling Prime Rib Cheesesteak has been described as “to die for!” Using REAL Wisconsin cheese (to do otherwise would of course be an infernal sin), freshly sliced premium meats, and locally baked bread, these perfectly toasted sandwiches are the ideal crunchy munch for your next lunch.
name: Inferno Subs
